<section id="roadmap" class="relative z-[2] bg-[var(--paper)] py-12 md:py-20">
  <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">

    <!-- Section head -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[1fr_2fr] gap-5 md:gap-16 mb-10 md:mb-14 items-end">
      <div>
        <div class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[11px] tracking-[.3em] text-[var(--moss)] uppercase">IV &middot; Roadmap</div>
        <h2 class="font-[var(--display)] font-normal mt-3 mb-0 leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.01em] text-[var(--ink)]"
            style="font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,56px)" data-ko-block>
          나무는 계속<br/>자라납니다
        </h2>
        <h2 class="font-[var(--display)] font-normal mt-3 mb-0 leading-[1.05] tracking-[-0.01em] text-[var(--ink)]"
            style="font-size:clamp(24px,4vw,56px)" data-en-block>
          The tree keeps<br/>growing
        </h2>
      </div>
      <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-base leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)] max-w-[560px] m-0" data-ko-block>검증(Verify) &rarr; 확장(Expand) &rarr; 연결(Connect) — 세 계절을 거쳐 Gopedia는 한 그루의 나무에서 한 조직의 신경계로 자랍니다.</p>
      <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-base leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)] max-w-[560px] m-0" data-en-block>Verify &rarr; Expand &rarr; Connect — across three seasons, Gopedia grows from a single tree into the nervous system of an entire organization.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline -->
    <div class="relative pt-8 pb-6 md:pt-14 md:pb-10">
      <!-- Horizontal connector line (hidden on mobile) -->
      <div class="absolute top-[50%] left-0 right-0 h-px bg-[var(--rule)] -translate-y-1/2 hidden md:block"></div>

      <div class="relative grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">

        <!-- Now · Verify -->
        <article class="relative bg-[var(--paper)] border border-[var(--rule)] p-6">
          <div class="absolute -top-[7px] left-6 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[var(--moss)] border border-[var(--moss)]"></div>
          <div class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[10.5px] tracking-[.25em] text-[var(--moss)] uppercase">Now &middot; Verify</div>
          <h4 class="font-[var(--display)] font-medium leading-[1.15] mt-2 mb-2.5 text-[var(--ink)]"
              style="font-size:clamp(16px,2vw,26px)" data-ko-block><em class="italic text-[var(--moss)]">뿌리</em>를 단단히</h4>
          <h4 class="font-[var(--display)] font-medium leading-[1.15] mt-2 mb-2.5 text-[var(--ink)]"
              style="font-size:clamp(16px,2vw,26px)" data-en-block>Tighten the <em class="italic text-[var(--moss)]">roots</em></h4>
          <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-sm leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)] m-0 mb-3.5" data-ko-block>정확한 인용, 측정 가능한 IR 품질, 출처 추적이 가능한 답변. 나무가 흔들려도 뿌리는 흔들리지 않게.</p>
          <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-sm leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)] m-0 mb-3.5" data-en-block>Accurate citations, measurable IR quality, traceable provenance. The canopy may sway — the roots must not.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
            <span class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[10.5px] text-[var(--bark-2)] border border-[var(--rule)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Citation</span>
            <span class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[10.5px] text-[var(--bark-2)] border border-[var(--rule)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">IR Eval</span>
            <span class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[10.5px] text-[var(--bark-2)] border border-[var(--rule)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Provenance</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Next · Expand -->
        <article class="relative bg-[var(--paper)] border border-[var(--rule)] p-6">
          <div class="absolute -top-[7px] left-6 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[var(--paper)] border border-[var(--moss)]"></div>
          <div class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[10.5px] tracking-[.25em] text-[var(--moss)] uppercase">Next &middot; Expand</div>
          <h4 class="font-[var(--display)] font-medium leading-[1.15] mt-2 mb-2.5 text-[var(--ink)]"
              style="font-size:clamp(16px,2vw,26px)" data-ko-block><em class="italic text-[var(--moss)]">가지</em>를 사방으로</h4>
          <h4 class="font-[var(--display)] font-medium leading-[1.15] mt-2 mb-2.5 text-[var(--ink)]"
              style="font-size:clamp(16px,2vw,26px)" data-en-block>Branches in <em class="italic text-[var(--moss)]">every direction</em></h4>
          <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-sm leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)] m-0 mb-3.5" data-ko-block>코드·이미지·표·음성까지 — 텍스트 너머의 잎사귀들을 같은 줄기에 매답니다. 멀티모달 RAG, 코드 그래프, 다이어그램 이해.</p>
          <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-sm leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)] m-0 mb-3.5" data-en-block>Code, images, tables, audio — leaves beyond text, hung on the same stem. Multimodal RAG, code graph, diagram understanding.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
            <span class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[10.5px] text-[var(--bark-2)] border border-[var(--rule)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Multimodal</span>
            <span class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[10.5px] text-[var(--bark-2)] border border-[var(--rule)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Code Graph</span>
            <span class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[10.5px] text-[var(--bark-2)] border border-[var(--rule)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Diagrams</span>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- Later · Connect -->
        <article class="relative bg-[var(--paper)] border border-[var(--rule)] border-dashed p-6">
          <div class="absolute -top-[7px] left-6 w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-[var(--paper)] border border-dashed border-[var(--moss)]"></div>
          <div class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[10.5px] tracking-[.25em] text-[var(--moss)] uppercase">Later &middot; Connect</div>
          <h4 class="font-[var(--display)] font-medium leading-[1.15] mt-2 mb-2.5 text-[var(--ink)]"
              style="font-size:clamp(16px,2vw,26px)" data-ko-block><em class="italic text-[var(--moss)]">숲</em>을 이루다</h4>
          <h4 class="font-[var(--display)] font-medium leading-[1.15] mt-2 mb-2.5 text-[var(--ink)]"
              style="font-size:clamp(16px,2vw,26px)" data-en-block>Become a <em class="italic text-[var(--moss)]">forest</em></h4>
          <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-sm leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)] m-0 mb-3.5" data-ko-block>나무 한 그루가 아닌 숲. 부서·자회사·파트너 사이에서 지식이 안전하게 오가는 신경계로 진화합니다.</p>
          <p class="font-[var(--serif)] text-sm leading-[1.7] text-[var(--ink-2)] m-0 mb-3.5" data-en-block>Not one tree, but a forest. Knowledge flows safely between teams, subsidiaries, and partners — an organizational nervous system.</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1.5">
            <span class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[10.5px] text-[var(--bark-2)] border border-[var(--rule)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Federation</span>
            <span class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[10.5px] text-[var(--bark-2)] border border-[var(--rule)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Agents</span>
            <span class="font-[var(--mono)] text-[10.5px] text-[var(--bark-2)] border border-[var(--rule)] px-2 py-0.5 rounded-full">Governance</span>
          </div>
        </article>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
